members.member:


Add a templated recordTarget to "ClinicalDocument.recordTarget"

Templates must be with constraint : NPFIT-000083#Role 

Any template within theNPFIT_000083_Role is permitted


            template rt = new template();
            doc.AddRecordTarget(rt);



            /// The template to be used for the record target

example.code:
template author = new template();
HL7V3_TS authorTime =  new HL7V3_TS(DateTime.Now());

doc.AddAuthor(author,authorTime);
